  "name": "Divine Retribution",
  "desc": "With a last word before you fall unconscious, this spell inflicts radiant damage to your attacker equal to 1d8 + the amount of damage you took from the triggering attack. If the attacker is a fiend or undead, it takes an extra 1d8 radiant damage. The creature then must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or become stunned for 1 minute. At the end of each of its turns, the creature can make another Constitution saving throw. On a successful save, it is no longer stunned.",
  "level": 1,
  "higher_level": "When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 1st.",
